{"word":"G3946 - παρόμοιος - parómoios - par-om'-oy-os - Like","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παρόμοιος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">parómoios</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-om'-oy-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Like</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"போல - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"like"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and <a href=\"#/G3664 - ὅμοιος - hómoios - hom'-oy-os/3664\">G3664</a>; <i>alike nearly</i>, that is, <i>similar:</i> - like.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3664/3664\">G3664</a>, <a href=\"#/G3665/3665\">G3665</a>, <a href=\"#/G3666/3666\">G3666</a>, <a href=\"#/G3667/3667\">G3667</a>, <a href=\"#/G3668/3668\">G3668</a>, <a href=\"#/G3669/3669\">G3669</a>, <a href=\"#/G3670/3670\">G3670</a>, <a href=\"#/G3945/3945\">G3945</a>, <a href=\"#/G3946/3946\">G3946</a>, <a href=\"#/G871/871\">G871</a>"}]}